This is a password hasher tool to run this tool you need to run it by enetring in the command line 

            python passwordcracker.py --type <hash_type> --wordlist <path_to_wordlist> <hash>


            this would allow the code to run 

            If password is found it will show the output as 

            Success! The password is: password123
  

            If it fails to find the password the output would be

            Password not found.


For Example 

python passwordcracker.py --type md5 --wordlist rockyou.txt 5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99
